   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Iran Banks Facility</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project is to provide credit facilities of up to $10 million each (the Facilities) to two Iranian private banks (the Banks)  Karafarin Bank (Karafarin) and Saman Bank (Saman).  The Banks are expected to use the proceeds to increase their working capital and term lending to hard-currency generating exporters and trading companies as well as to expand their other corporate and retail services.</narrative>
  </description>
